column2: ID for suite of sites or experiments
column3: Name of experiment, field test or survey
column10: Climate replication number for multiple realizations of weather data (ask Alex)
column14: Management regimen ID, for multiple management regimens per RAP
column15: Names of institutions involved in collection of field or survey data
column16: Crop rotation indicator (=1 to indicate that this is a continuous, multi-year simulation, =0 for single year simulations)
column27: Observed total above-ground biomass at harvest
column45: Short name of crop model used for simulations (e.g., DSSAT, APSIM, Aquacrop, STICS, etc.)
column46: Model name and version number of the crop model used to generate simulated outputs
column48: Simulated above-ground biomass at harvest, dry matter
column53: Total precipitation from planting to harvest
column56: Simulated N leached up to harvest maturity
column57: Transpiration, cumulative from planting to harvest
column58: Evaporation,soil, cumulative from planting to harvest
